<br>
Why am I a racist?  Why are you allowed to make statements such as, &quot;Arabs have no work ethic&quot;, and be guilty of nothing more than a simple generalization, while my opinions regarding the motivations and ideology of Arab Muslims make me a racist?  Or even just ignore the double standard and make your case... dig up quotes if you care to, I'm curious how you're going to justify this one.<br>
<br>
To help you a little, I'll provide a definition:<br>
<br>
racism<br>
<br>
n 1: the prejudice that members of one race are intrinsically superior to members of other races 2: discriminatory or abusive behavior towards members of another race<br>
